race.comment: BERNARD SHAW (4) Finished on top last start at this track. Has early speed and positions nicely. Will be competitive. ALABRAZ (3) Ran 10th last time at the track. Can give this a shake. JEMER (12) Came in 5th last run at this venue. Definite claims. LAST ADDITION (20) Tidy effort when 3rd last time here and racing over a longer distance. Jockey Muhammad Aldaham and trainer Thamer Aldaihani enjoy a strong success rate. Deserves consideration.
